skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: starship captain
des: starship captain is an interactive scenario that transports you to the captains chair, and takes you on an intergalactic adventure assisted by the ships computer. You may ask the computer to raise shields, scan for enemies, engage warp or fire photon torpedoes. If you feel in danger at any time you may ask the computer to transport you home. An adventure lies ahead, just ask the computer to transport you to the ship.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
